text: Sympleurotis albofasciatus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Julio and Monné in 2005. It is known from Mexico.BioLib.cz - Sympleurotis albofasciatus. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 2005
